text: "Ob-La-Di, Ob-La-Da" is a 1968 song by The Beatles and taken from their ninth studio album The Beatles. It went to number 1 in Australia, Austria, Germany, Japan, New Zealand and Switzerland. It went to number 27 in Canada and number 49 in the United States in 1976. ==References== Category:1968 songs Category:The Beatles songs
title: Ob-La-Di, Ob-La-Da
